\c 65
\s Vanomukira Jehovha vacharohwa
\p
\v 1 Ndakatsvakwa nevasina kundibvunza; ndakawanikwa nevasina kunditsvaka; ndakati: Nditarirei, nditarirei, kurudzi rwusina kudanwa nezita rangu.
\v 2 Ndakatambanudzira maoko angu zuva rese kuvanhu vanopanduka, vanofamba nenzira isina kunaka, vachitevera ndangariro dzavo;
\v 3 vanhu vanogara vachinditsamwisa pachiso changu, vanoita zvibairo mumabindu, uye vanopisa zvipfungaidzo zvinonhuhwira pamusoro pezvitinha;
\v 4 vanogara pakati pemakuva, uye vanorara panzvimbo dzakavandika; vanodya nyama yenguruve, uye muto wezvinhu zvinonyangadza mumidziyo yavo.
\v 5 Vanoti: Mira wega, usaswedera kwandiri, nokuti ndiri mutsvene kupfuura iwe. Ava utsi mumhino dzangu, moto unopfuta zuva rese.
\v 6 Tarirai zvakanyorwa pamberi pangu: Handinganyarari, asi ndichatsiva, zvirokwazvo ndichatsiva pachipfuva chavo,
\v 7 zvakaipa zvenyu, nezvakaipa zvemadzibaba enyu pamwe chete, anoreva Jehovha, vakapisa zvipfungaidzo zvinonhuhwira pamusoro pemakomo, nekundinyomba pamusoro pezvikomo, naizvozvo ndichayera basa ravo rekutanga pachipfuva chavo.
\v 8 Anoreva seizvi Jehovha: Waini itsva sezvainowaikwa musumbu \add remazambiringa\add*, \add umwe\add* akati: Usariparadza, nokuti ropafadzo iri mariri, ndichaita saizvozvo nekuda kwevaranda vangu, kuti ndisavaparadza vese.
\v 9 Zvino ndichabudisa mbeu kubva muna Jakove, uye kubva muna Judha mugari wenhaka yemakomo angu, zvino vasanangurwa vangu vachaagara nhaka, uye varanda vangu vachagaramo.
\v 10 Zvino Sharoni richava danga remapoka, nemupata weAkori nzvimbo yerara mombe pasi, yevanhu vangu vakanditsvaka.
\p
\v 11 Asi imwi munosiya Jehovha, munokanganwa gomo rangu dzvene, munogadzirira Rombo Rakanaka tafura, nekuzadzira Mugumo waini yakavhenganiswa.
\v 12 Ndichakuverengerai kumunondo, uye mese muchakotamira kubayiwa; nokuti pandakadana hamuna kupindura; pandakataura hamuna kunzwa; asi makaita zvakaipa pameso pangu, mukasarudza zvandisina kufadzwa nazvo.
\p
\v 13 Naizvozvo anoreva seizvi Ishe Jehovha: Tarirai, varanda vangu vachadya, asi imwi muchava nenzara; tarirai, varanda vangu vachanwa, asi imwi muchava nenyota; tarirai, varanda vangu vachafara, asi imwi muchanyadziswa;
\v 14 tarirai, varanda vangu vachaimba nemufaro wemoyo, asi imwi muchachema nekurwadziwa kwemoyo, muchaungudza nekuputsika kwemweya.
\v 15 Zvino muchasiya zita renyu rive chakatukwa kuvasanangurwa vangu, nokuti Ishe Jehovha achakuurayayi, asi achadaidza varanda vake nerimwe zita;
\v 16 kuti ani nani anozviropafadza panyika, achazviropafadza kuna Mwari wachokwadi; neanopika panyika achapika naMwari wechokwadi, nokuti matambudziko ekutanga akanganikwa, uye nokuti akavanzika pameso angu.
\p
\v 17 Nokuti tarirai, ndinosika matenga matsva nenyika itsva; zvinhu zvekare hazvingarangarirwi, kana kupinda mundangariro.
\v 18 Asi farai mufarisise nekusingaperi sezvandinosika, nokuti tarirai, ndinosika Jerusarema \add kuva\add* mufaro, nevanhu varo \add kuva\add* mufaro.
\v 19 Zvino ndichafara muJerusarema, nekuva nemufaro nevanhu vangu; uye inzwi rekuungudza harichazonzwikwi mariri kana inzwi rekuchema.
\v 20 Hapangazovi nerushiye rwemazuva \add mashoma\add*, kana mutana asina kuzadzisa mazuva ake; nokuti mwana achafa ava nemakore zana, nemutadzi ane makore zana achatukwa.
\v 21 Zvino vachavaka dzimba ndokugara; uye vachadzvara minda yemizambiringa ndokudya zvemichero yayo.
\v 22 Havangavaki umwe ndokugara, havangadzvari umwe ndokudya, nokuti semazuva emuti, \add akadaro\add* mazuva evanhu vangu. Zvino vanhu vangu vachanakirwa nebasa remaoko avo nguva refu.
\v 23 Havangashingairiri pasina, kana kuzviberekera dambudziko, nokuti ivo imbeu yemuropafadzwa waJehovha, nechibereko chavo pamwe navo.
\v 24 Zvino zvichaitika vasati vadana kuti ndichapindura, vachiri kutaura ndichanzwa.
\v 25 Bere negwayana zvichafura pamwe chete, uye shumba ichadya uswa senzombe, uye guruva richava zvekudya zvenyoka. Hazvingakuvadzi kana kuparadza mugomo rangu dzvene rese, anoreva Jehovha.
